{"title":"足迹在这里遭遇","authors":["曲有源"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":4,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"足迹在这里遭遇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曲有源"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我又来到石狮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻找"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二年前陷进泥浆路上的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的被推土机推到一边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的被碎石压在下面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即便离开了马路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也没逃脱打桩机的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一击"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今这些溃不成队的足迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"召集起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我才发觉有点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陌生新奇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来重新排列一下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一行行生动的诗句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和狮子的目光一致"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在街心广场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个石狮塑像的身旁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看他面前的楼房"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都像逞疯似地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪一栋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都比他高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你把瞳孔的旋钮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像望远镜那样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"调整一下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让视线和石狮的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就会看到更高的建筑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在后面"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}